        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$3(x-2) + 1(x+2) = 4 \\implies 3x - 6 + x + 2 = 4 \\implies 4x - 4 = 4 \\implies 4x = 8 \\implies x = 2$. However, $x=2$ makes denominators zero, so extraneous. No solution."
